title: Ladies and Gentlemen The Grateful Dead (Arista 2000)
description:
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN . . . THE GRATEFUL DEAD!
Live at the Fillmore East, New York City, April 1971

4 CD set released in 2000 by Arista.

It has been released a few times over the past 14 years; my version is the Arista original set which was in HDCD. I don't know how they might have remastered it, it was great the first time.

This is an excellent set -- lots of Pigpen, not much overt psychedelia but don't be fooled. Musically it's a little spotty but in the end all is forgiven.

This is the third and final version of this torrent, so it must be perfect.
